<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Client Agreement Form</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<h1>Client Agreement Form</h1>

<form>

<p>
<label>Client Name</label><br>
<input type="text" style="width:400px;">
</p>

<p>
<label>Email</label><br>
<input type="email" style="width:400px;">
</p>

<p>
<label>Phone</label><br>
<input type="text" style="width:400px;">
</p>

<p>
<label>Property Address</label><br>
<input type="text" style="width:600px;">
</p>

<p>
<label>Inspection Type</label><br>
<select style="width:300px;">
<option>Building Inspection</option>
<option>Pest Inspection</option>
<option>Building & Pest Inspection</option>
<option>Handover Inspection</option>
</select>
</p>

<p>
<label>Inspection Date</label><br>
<input type="date">
</p>

<h2>Agreement Terms</h2>

<div style="background:white;padding:20px;border-radius:10px;max-width:900px;line-height:1.6;">

<p>
The inspection will be carried out in accordance with Australian Standards where applicable.
</p>

<p>
The inspection is a visual assessment only and does not include destructive testing or inspection of concealed areas.
</p>

<p>
The report is prepared solely for the client named in this agreement and must not be relied upon by third parties.
</p>

<p>
The inspection may not identify all defects, faults, damage, pest activity, or conditions that are hidden, inaccessible, or not visible at the time of inspection.
</p>

<p>
The client acknowledges that the inspection is limited by access, visibility, weather conditions, and other factors beyond the inspector's control.
</p>

<p>
By proceeding with this inspection, the client agrees to the inspection terms and conditions.
</p>

</div>

<br>

<p>
<input type="checkbox">
I have read and agree to the terms and conditions.
</p>

<p>
<label>Client Signature</label><br>
<input type="text" placeholder="Type Full Name" style="width:400px;">
</p>

<p>
<label>Date Signed</label><br>
<input type="date">
</p>

<br>

<button type="submit">Submit Agreement</button>

</form>

<br><br>

<a href="forms.html">← Back to Forms</a>

</body>
</html>
